      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic restoration. The engine currently runs roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, while the body shows notable rust patches and several dents. The interior has sustained heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is an ideal candidate for a dedicated parts car or a full-scale restoration project for a skilled mechanic.",
