    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes. Each body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting the factory-original tolerances. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, devoid of the typical wear or creasing found in used examples. The factory-fresh scent persists, and every tactile control\u2014from the knurled knobs to the digital displays\u2014operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. The engine bay is immaculate, and the vehicle drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a brand-new car. All service intervals have been strictly adhered to, documented by a comprehensive folder of records. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
